OL,4,CBatley school protests: Identifying
OL,5,Cprophet row teacher 'unacceptable'
OL,6, Sharing the identity of a teacher who
OL,7, showed pupils an "offensive" cartoon of
OL,8, the Prophet Muhammad could result in
OL,9, police action, a watchdog has warned.
OL,11,FProtests were held outside Batley
OL,12,FGrammar School, where the staff member
OL,13,Fwas suspended after complaints.
OL,15,FBaroness Kishwer Falkner said making a
OL,16,Fteacher fear for their safety was
OL,17,F"simply unacceptable".
OL,19,FThe Equality and Human Rights
OL,20,FCommission chair said the school "ought
OL,21,Fto be trusted" to take action.
